<item>
            <title>[LU-18855] Change ct_open_by_fid to use new open by fid method</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18855</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The function &lt;tt&gt;liblustgreapi_hsm.c:ct_open_by_fid&lt;/tt&gt; uses the old implementation of open by fid. This should be change to call llapi_open_by_fid_at directly.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The will make the &lt;tt&gt;open_by_fid_fd&lt;/tt&gt; field in the &lt;tt&gt;struct hsm_copytool_private&lt;/tt&gt;&#160;obsolete. Although I don&apos;t think we can&apos;t remove the field, we can stop initializing it.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
